summary: All I see from these season 8 teasers is that they're trying to drill into y'all heads that sansa is a hella relevant character,...
body:
All I see from these season 8 teasers is that they’re trying to drill into y'all heads that sansa is a hella relevant character, that Jon is still going to belong to the Starks and that the starks are more tight than ever! (Nope, no stark!bowl is going to happen, I’m sorry)

Think about it.. they could shoot the same hype teaser from a targ pov, Jon and Daenerys in targ attire representing the last dragons of their house, even Jon caressing Daenerys belly and then the 2 of them looking worried towards the ice and the darkness reaching them as we see in this teaser, I mean.. we could have had a targ feast but we don’t, we are presented with the starks over and over again so..

A time for wolves is coming:)
